@Driver for the SD/MMC part of the Winbond W83L518D/W83L519D Integrated Media
Reader.
@
text
@/*	$OpenBSD$	*/
/*	$NetBSD: w83l518dvar.h,v 1.1 2009/09/30 20:44:50 jmcneill Exp $ */

